  "title": "Grassy Syrian Duck-Confit-Leg Clay-Pot-Cook",
  "description": "A crumbly, date-night Syrian dish featuring tender duck confit leg, all clay-pot-cooked with a hint of mint and parsley, served with a side of garlic flatbread.",
